# SkyWeb Change Log

Detailed phase and transition history for SkyWeb Analytics. The README stays focused on current status and developer commands.

## DN-7.1 — Saved Views/Dashboards Build Stabilization

- Fixed `SkyWebDashboardsService.UpdateDashboardItemAsync` local variable shadowing that caused CS0136 during `dotnet build`.
- Cleared the nullable saved-view handoff warning in `SkyWebSavedViewsService.SaveViewAsync` by falling back to the normalized requested view key.
- Kept the DN-7 endpoint contract unchanged; this is a compile/build stabilization patch only.

## DN-7 — Saved Views and Dashboards in C#

- Added native C# saved-view endpoints.
- Added native C# dashboard and dashboard-item endpoints.
- Narrowed the SkyServer proxy bridge to alerts and signal queues only.

## DN-6 — SkyWeb Profile and Preferences in C#

- Added native C# profile, dashboard preferences, and alert preference endpoints.

## DN-5.2 — Indicator Series Regclass/NaN Fix

- Cast PostgreSQL `to_regclass` checks to text.
- Scrubbed PostgreSQL numeric `NaN` values to JSON-safe nulls for indicator series responses.

## DN-5 — Authentication in C#

- Added native C# login, logout, change-password, me, and permissions endpoints.

## DN-4 — Public Macro REST Endpoints in C#

- Added native public macro summary, views, columns, latest, indicators, and series endpoints.

## Phase 8.8 — Alert Rule UX Polish

- Added alert rule search/filter/sort, inline edit, clone, safer remove confirmation, and validation polish.
